${alignc 18}${font Droid Sans Mono:pixelsize=23}${color2}${time %H:%M}${color}${font}
${alignc 5}${font Droid Sans Mono:pixelsize=11}${time %a %d %b %Y}${font}
${alignc 5}${font Droid Sans Mono:pixelsize=11}${texeci 60 py /home/georgi/.dotfiles/conky/mail.pyc}${font}
